    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Subj: Request for Information on Sightings of Unidentified Aerial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Phenomena in the Dallas-Ft. Worth Area",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "1. A subcommittee of the [REDACTED] has recently been established in the Dallas-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Ft. Worth area. [REDACTED] is a private, non-profit organization directed by",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Major Donald E. Keyhoe, USMC (Ret) from the National Headquarters in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Washington, D. C. The purpose of the organization is to conduct scientific",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "investigation of Unidentified Flying Objects. It now has 14,000 associate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "members in 50 states. The organization is not interested in the alleged",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "psychic, occult, mystical, or religious aspects of UFO phenomena.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "2. [REDACTED] subcommittees, of which there are 30 in the United",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "States, are composed of qualified individuals in technical or investigative",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "fields, who are selected and appointed by the Washington office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "3. [REDACTED] is currently working closely with the Colorado Project,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "a comprehensive study of UFO's begun in November 1966, by a group of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "distinguished scientists at the University of Colorado under a U. S. Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Force contract.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "4. The local subcommittee earnestly solicits your support in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "reporting to the Committee Chairman any UFO sightings occurring in this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "area. It is especially important that the NICAP committee be contacted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "immediately in cases of reported UFO sightings where photographs have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
